room_title: Escape room "S.W.A.T." by Escape Room NJ in New York
room_description: The Director of the CIA has just briefed you on the case - it's a terror threat, and the terrorist has the bomb planted at his apartment. If it detonates, half of the city will be left in ruins. Your team has been selected to lead this operation, and the task is to gain entry, assess the situation, locate the terrorist and disarm the bomb. When you arrive at the apartment and take a glance under the door, you are shocked to see the bomb right in front of your eyes - hiding in plain sight. But this seems too easy...
